  "detailed_description": "<h1>The Birdie Story!</h1><p>Being a little nestling, Birdie listened to the story about a Golden Grain many times. Growing up he dreamed of finding the treasure, however, he didn’t have enough strength and determination. Now, when he is grown up, he decided to fulfill his childhood dream and find this artifact.<br><br>Join our hero, to experience a wonderful adventure in various and colorful locations. Starting in a modest forest, throughout rich castles, down to the secrets of the deep sea. Help Birdie defeat the threats he might encounter, and with help of other travelers lead him to the Golden Grain.<br><br>In Go! Birdie you have to collect all fruits in grid-based, maze-like levels. Animals will try to stop you, so avoid them or pick up right power-ups to fight back. There are bonus levels where your only enemy is time. You can either maximize your score by beating whole game at once, or play it from chapter to chapter.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480470/extras/81bf33ca8b959eb6b7f99d56f65a8e5e.poster.avif?t=1671201368\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480470/extras/81bf33ca8b959eb6b7f99d56f65a8e5e.webm?t=1671201368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480470/extras/81bf33ca8b959eb6b7f99d56f65a8e5e.mp4?t=1671201368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect all the fruits under time pressure!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480470/extras/4fcc0e9004ffff387f3273c021182ed1.poster.avif?t=1671201368\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480470/extras/4fcc0e9004ffff387f3273c021182ed1.webm?t=1671201368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480470/extras/4fcc0e9004ffff387f3273c021182ed1.mp4?t=1671201368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Relax with your friends! Collect all fruits with your mate.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480470/extras/4de9588c51619359ecbedb68520473dd.poster.avif?t=1671201368\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480470/extras/4de9588c51619359ecbedb68520473dd.webm?t=1671201368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480470/extras/4de9588c51619359ecbedb68520473dd.mp4?t=1671201368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Power-ups gives you unique abilities which help you fight enemies.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480470/extras/562dcfb11ba37699b10b5300f405f7be.poster.avif?t=1671201368\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480470/extras/562dcfb11ba37699b10b5300f405f7be.webm?t=1671201368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480470/extras/562dcfb11ba37699b10b5300f405f7be.mp4?t=1671201368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Customize your Birdie !</li></ul>",
